        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 5b: immunogold EM of mouse DRG neurons showed GINIP (Gαi-interacting protein, gene PHF24) localized at the membranes of synaptic vesicles.. Experimental description: mice were used for all experiments. \"Sixteen TAFA4Venus heterozygous (±) knock in mice\", \"Twelve 3-week-old GINIP mice\", Six CD1 mice (n = 3 for LM; n = 3 for EM), as control animals to verify peptidergic and non-peptidergic marker expression in genetically unmodified animals." ;
